text: Þreo hund hida hyrð to Eorpeburnan & XXIIII hida to Hæstingaceastre hyrþ V hund hida & to Læwe hyrþ twelf hund hida.
& to Burham hyrþ seofan hund hida & XX hida.
To Cisseceastre hyrþ XV hund hida.
Þonne hyrþ to Portceastre V hund hida & oþer healf hund hida hyrþ to Hamtune.
& to Wintaceastre hyrþ feower & twentig hund hida & to Wiltune hyrþ feowertine hund hida.
& to Tissanbyrig hyrþ V hund hida & to Tweoneam hyrþ V hund hida butan XXX hidan.
& to Werham hyrþ XVI hund hida & to Brydian hyrþ eahta hund hida butan feowertigan hidan.
& to Eaxanceastre hyrþ feower & XXX hida & VII hund hida & to Halganwille hyrþ þreo hund hida.
& to Hlidan hyrþ oþer healf hund hida butan X hidan & to Pilletune hyrþ feower hund hida butan XL hidan.
& to Weced hyrð V hund hida & XIII hida & to Axanbrycge hyrþ feower hund hida.
& to Lengen hyrþ C hida & to Langport hyrð VI hund hida & to Baðan hyrð tyn hund hida.
& twelf hund hida hyrð to Mealdmesbyring & to Crecgelade hyrþ XIIII hund hida & XV hund hida to Oxnaforda.
& to Wælingforda hyrð XXIIII hund hida & XVI hund hida hyrð to Buccingahamme.
& to Sceaftesige hyrð X hund hida & VI hund hida hyrþ to Escingum & to Suþriganaweorce hyrþ eahtatyne hund hida.
